As Allen Wamack , a 15-year - old boy , drove by a Negro schoolhouse , he called out " school butter " ( an insult meaning a cobbing , or a whipping ) .
The students came out and fired several shots at him ; he shot back , hitting two students . 0 0 As news of outlaw Jesse James reached the East Coast , young boys started to imitate him .
