After some of his dormmates urinated on his mattress during hazing , Robert B. Bechtel , a 22-year - old student proctor at Swarthmore College , returned to his Wharton Hall dorm with a shotgun and killed fellow student , 19-year - old Francis Holmes Strozier .
Betchtel was acquitted of murder by reason of insanity and spent five years in a psychiatric hospital .
