, Larry J. Harmon , armed with a rifle , killed 68-year - old caretaker , Hilary Kunzon , who came upon him wrecking St. Aloysius Roman Catholic Church , then fled onto the campus of Gonzaga University , where he wounded four more people before he was shot and killed by police .
