2 0 As students fled their rooms , after a homemade firebomb set a minor blaze on the sixth floor hallway of Bursley Hall dormitory , 22-year - old psychology student , Leo E. Kelly Jr. , fired a sawn - off 12-gauge shotgun at his University of Michigan schoolmates at point - blank range .
