Cokeville Elementary School hostage crisis : 43-year - old former town marshal David Young , and his 47-year - old wife , Doris Young , took 136 children and eighteen adults hostage at Cokeville Elementary School .
Doris Young accidentally detonated a bomb she was carrying during the standoff , injuring herself and 73 others .
David Young then shot and killed Doris , shot and wounded a teacher , and then committed suicide .
