3 14-year - old Kristofer Hans intended to shoot his French teacher at Fergus High School , for a failing grade .
Instead , Henrietta Smith , who was substituting for LaVonne Simonfy , was shot in the face and died .
Hans fired several other shots as he fled , wounding vice principal John Moffatt , and two students .
He then ran about a mile to his home , where he was arrested after the police surrounded his house .
A classmate said Hans had repeatedly threatened to kill Ms. Simonfy , saying , " I 'm going to blow Simonfy 's head off . "
He was charged as an adult , convicted and sentenced to 206 years in prison .
