21 Columbine High School massacre : 18-year - old Eric Harris and 17-year - old Dylan Klebold , students at Columbine High School , killed twelve students and one teacher .
They injured 21 additional people , and three more were injured while attempting to escape the school .
The pair committed suicide in the library after a brief gunfight with police at the end of the massacre .
Eric and Dylan used a 9 mm Hi Point Carbine rifle , a Savage 67H pump - action shotgun ( sawed off ) , multiple pipe bombs , propane tanks , gasoline bombs , etc .
Klebold used a Intratec TEC - DC9 semi - automatic pistol , a stevens 311d double barreled sawed - off shotgun multiple pipe bombs , Molotov cocktails , and propane tanks . 0 6 15-year - old student Thomas " T.J. " Solomon Jr. , wounded six students at Heritage High School .
